description:
Clairol Shimmer Lights Original Conditioning Shampoo brightens white and gray hair. Shampoos away yellow, and refreshes faded highlights.<br />
<br />
Let your lights shine! Bring out the shimmering highlights in your hair with Clairol Shimmer Lights Original Conditioning Shampoo. A protein-enriched color enhancing shampoo that tones down brassiness on blonde/gray hair. It shampoos away yellow and refreshes faded highlighted hair. Maintains and refreshes cool, ash-toned haircolor. Shampoo leaves hair shiny without residue. &nbsp;&nbsp;
